<p>We decided before release 2.0 Alpha (very soon), on which we have been working hard lately, to devote some time to the 1.4.x branch, so meet release 1.4.6.<br>
The main works were aimed at stability of work + on safety, now the OutdatedExtrasCheck plugin takes information from the server, thus information on additions that have security problems will appear on the dashboard, which will give even more chances to learn about possible problems with security and fix it promptly.<br>
<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/669491/47910458-9c659400-de9b-11e8-9625-9b512d37b4dc.png"><img width="384" alt="146ajaxsearch" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/669491/47910458-9c659400-de9b-11e8-9625-9b512d37b4dc.png" style="max-width:100%;"></a></p>
